My favorite subject...WEAPONS!<br>
<br>
Okay I solo quite a bit at times and use the following.<br>
<br>
Truncheon of Doom (procs 50% slow every battle)<br>
Primal Velium Warsword (avatar-enough said)<br>
Trident of the Seep Seas (10% slow and 500 dot over 25 ticks, great for those runners if you don't have a ku'juch)<br>
Bloodpoint (makes bandages by the carload)<br>
Silver Whip of Rage (150 point dam rune)<br>
Journeyman's Stick (low end tash)<br>
Primal War Lance (2h version of avatar after using truncheon above)<br>
Kunzar Ku'Juch (engulfing darkness a soloing warriors best friend)<br>
Fungi Tunic (regen!!!)<br>
Sarnak Warhammer (Stun for those pesky casting type mobs)<br>
Stun Whip (bahh think is a low end one)<br>
<br>
and 61% haste earring of endless speed and eyepatch of plunder.<br>
<br>
Oh yes and what I call my equalizer when I go into berserking mode and I want to get even.<br>
<br>
Twisted Steel Bastard Sword<br>
Properties MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO DROP   <br>
Type: Slots Weapon: Primary <br>
Armor Class 25 <br>
Weapon Skill 2HS <br>
Damage DMG: 53  DLY: 45  DPS: 23.78 (has damage bonus) <br>
Magic DMG None <br>
